  transformer enclosed between brackets (in this case [fv]). In order to get the feature vector you will have to 
  specify that you want the field (e.g., fl="*,[fv])  -->
  <transformer name="fv" class="ltr.ranking.LTRFeatureLoggerTransformerFactory" />



